    "body": "This is still an issue for me.\n\nI am using fish terminal with starship. It hangs until i press CTRL+C\n\nif i try to connect to another machine directly in fish shell it hangs\n\n```\n$ ssh desktop\n[ERROR] - (starship::print): Under a 'dumb' terminal (TERM=dumb).\n^C⏎\n$\n```\n\nNow i disabled RemoteCommand=fish section and now i have to type out fish everytime i enter ssh.\nIf there is a workaround i would be super happy.",
